quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  16,7,"Watahmilu athqalakum ilabaladin lam takoonoo baligheehi illa bishiqqial-anfusi inna rabbakum laraoofun raheem"
  16,8,"Walkhayla walbighalawalhameera litarkabooha wazeenatanwayakhluqu ma la taAAlamoon"
  16,9,"WaAAala Allahi qasdu assabeeliwaminha ja-irun walaw shaa lahadakumajmaAAeen"
  16,10,"Huwa allathee anzala mina assama-imaan lakum minhu sharabun waminhu shajarun feehituseemoon"